11#ifndef API_VIDEO_TRACK_SOURCE_PROXY_H_
12#define API_VIDEO_TRACK_SOURCE_PROXY_H_
13
14#include "api/media_stream_interface.h"
15#include "api/proxy.h"
16
17namespace webrtc {
18
19// Makes sure the real VideoTrackSourceInterface implementation is destroyed on
20// the signaling thread and marshals all method calls to the signaling thread.
21// TODO(deadbeef): Move this to .cc file and out of api/. What threads methods
22// are called on is an implementation detail.
23BEGIN_PROXY_MAP(VideoTrackSource)
24PROXY_PRIMARY_THREAD_DESTRUCTOR()
25PROXY_CONSTMETHOD0(SourceState, state)
26BYPASS_PROXY_CONSTMETHOD0(bool, remote)
27BYPASS_PROXY_CONSTMETHOD0(bool, is_screencast)
28PROXY_CONSTMETHOD0(absl::optional<bool>, needs_denoising)
29PROXY_METHOD1(bool, GetStats, Stats*)
30PROXY_SECONDARY_METHOD2(void,
31 AddOrUpdateSink,
32 rtc::VideoSinkInterface<VideoFrame>*,
33 const rtc::VideoSinkWants&)
34PROXY_SECONDARY_METHOD1(void, RemoveSink, rtc::VideoSinkInterface<VideoFrame>*)
35PROXY_METHOD1(void, RegisterObserver, ObserverInterface*)
36PROXY_METHOD1(void, UnregisterObserver, ObserverInterface*)
37PROXY_CONSTMETHOD0(bool, SupportsEncodedOutput)
38PROXY_SECONDARY_METHOD0(void, GenerateKeyFrame)
39PROXY_SECONDARY_METHOD1(void,
40 AddEncodedSink,
41 rtc::VideoSinkInterface<RecordableEncodedFrame>*)
42PROXY_SECONDARY_METHOD1(void,
43 RemoveEncodedSink,
44 rtc::VideoSinkInterface<RecordableEncodedFrame>*)
45END_PROXY_MAP()
46
47} // namespace webrtc
48
49#endif // API_VIDEO_TRACK_SOURCE_PROXY_H_
